Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎樣的垃圾隊伍  都能使其獲勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才經理人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初  初次見面  我是倉部勝代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:04.45,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倉部勝代  天才經理人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  之後就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部  部長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到罐頭小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何  都只剩下最後48小時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截稿日期已經不能再推遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我相信芥川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  文科系不是這樣打氣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  雖然是低潮期
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能一味消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打起精神  噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我一直都只是幫運動部打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文科系是第一次所以稍稍有點不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我老師了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我丈途就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也請叫我勝代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小勝代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管事情來龍去脈如何  她是在幫我打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是部長帶來的  有點那個啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿紙和筆都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要的話儘管和我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:56.90,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}中午12點 : 2小時過後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我先去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換  換衣服?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  在那扇門的後面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  還是想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這種程度就能寫20頁原稿的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要快點寫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專欄  連載  直接發表新作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  如果就這樣一直寫不出來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L O V E  芥川!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C U T E  丈途!  Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很高興  但麻煩你安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.80,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}下午1點 : 3小時過後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於芥川丈途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為截稿日期快到了所以請假了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像聽說因為低潮而被監禁在罐頭小屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他請假後清靜多了也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便也給我變成正常人多好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監禁?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  之前一直認為制服圍裙這種著裝很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來應該改變一下這觀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯很快就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次吃女生親手做的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多吃點  補充體力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  趁熱吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常補腦的勝代特製金槍魚眼珠湯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝代君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人身上在某種條件下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能變大6倍左右的器官是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男  男性生殖…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨  注意你的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瞳孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗的地方會變大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來對下答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還有時間打瞌睡  你還真是從容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在趕稿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  睡了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抓緊的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來拍寫不出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工口小說的色情作家的照片而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倉部勝代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  我去準備晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才經理人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是被打氣的人絕對會獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  有她打氣就可以說是獲得了勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個勝利無論何時都伴隨著代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是勝代應援的棒球部的悲慘下場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的手機  怎麼會在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}等…等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是丈途老師的經理人  叫倉部勝代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找丈途老師嗎  請稍候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是編輯先生打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在  說我不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他讓我說他不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣的  請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是電腦突然出了點問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  我是用手寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的家人去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍到好的照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就加油趕稿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  我不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒有寫作的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編輯其實也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事  丈途同學你一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請找回自信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這隻手的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我非寫原稿不可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}丈  丈途同學  不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會有截稿日期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  這種時間她還在努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微  再努力下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:26.33,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}上午8點 : 22小時過後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著勉強自己讀我的小說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  作為經理人必須
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解丈途同學所有的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  不會吧  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別  別過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到她居然叫了一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要認輸  加油  盡全力…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然做夢都在為我加油我很高興啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 我也睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來夏那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你和經理人都被關起來…了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  律  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能不能也幫我請個假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間實在是緊得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊…緊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的是太緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙著趕稿脫不開身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}難…難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫不開身?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.63,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雁字搦め:一種捆綁方法 引申為被事物纏身 不能自由行動之意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以…以你的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會有這種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我我我我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律 快背圓周率
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3.141592653589793238462633832795…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}不行了 我要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝代君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位於加拿大薩斯喀徹溫省北部的湖的名字是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O Oman…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說清楚點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman…Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.24,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這湖的日語發音就和小穴(omanko)發音一樣 勝代迫於無奈才改用E文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大聲點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再熱情點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像在戀人耳邊低聲訴說情話那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將要迎來高潮那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像喝著黎明的咖啡時那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:38.42,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去幫你跟老師請假 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  繼續繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  這是色情小說家芥川丈途的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}又來!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有催稿以外的要事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在聽到嗶～的聲音後留言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啵～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便接別人的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想我是你的經理人  所以就得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我這個笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再附贈個「笨蛋」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子沒救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.87,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}中午12點 : 26小時過後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小勝代嗎  門開著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠江同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我聽說在修羅場的作家很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就做便當帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那種事  剛好我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看  太丟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為時間不太夠  有些著急…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  畢竟她是偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很忙  卻為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現役頂級偶像親手做的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配上手上纏的創可貼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到得到別人的支持會這麼讓人高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太誇張了  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續寫稿吧  我來餵你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  味道如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我至今為止吃過的最好吃的便當了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼老師  加油寫稿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都是謠江同學的私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也  也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙嘴唇接觸了這雙筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙筷子又接觸了我的嘴唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等於是  我的嘴唇和那雙嘴唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是現實的破壞力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行得通  把這份激情投入作品中去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  被運動部的人拜託去給他們加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好精緻的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話  一起吃怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  我肚子都餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  繼續加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明差一點就可以想到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是完全沒有進展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  還是完全沒有思路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還不用著急  還有20個小時呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小時…那個…該寫多少頁好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要引出情慾  首先需要遮掩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後則需要若隱若現展露出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是基本嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神  用上我所有的感官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我現在感受到的這份感情 現實的激情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要把它們變成文字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偷看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  一不留神目光掃到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了作品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讀了丈途同學的很多作品  所以我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了作品創作  這種事是必要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:58.93,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}晚上9點 : 35小時過後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下12個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿寫得怎麼樣了  完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了  接下來就是真正的修羅場了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起  一分一秒目光也不能離開稿紙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快寫吧  我也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight oh! Fight oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go 丈途…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}果然還是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦汗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手  手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請賜予丈途同學的手以奇跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  寫出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我已經沒法描寫女孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  就連這套珍藏的服裝也不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  我已經打算封筆了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不行的  丈途同學是天才色情小說家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不寫色情小說怎麼行…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這麼放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這樣綁著  我怎麼能寫得出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是我是經理人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是說過火了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過無所謂了  已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回我總算是明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是女生所以才寫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我仔細想過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才肌肉同好會  高級健身家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健美肌肉～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位  為了丈途同學的色情小說家之路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情為他展示男人的美妙之處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是肌肉男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo 這是二頭肌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo 這是腹肌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是胸肌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到了  碰到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬  還很濕 而且好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油  芥川老師
